items.title: Authorities identify officer killed in burst of gunfire near CDC HQ, Emory campus
items.description: A police officer was killed after authorities say an active shooter opened fire near the CDC headquarters and Emory University's Atlanta campus.

items.title: Former FBI, CIA Director William H. Webster dies at 101
items.description: William H. Webster, who served as the head of both the FBI and the CIA in a career spanning the late 1970s to the early 1990s, has died. He was 101.

items.title: WATCH:  Active shooter reported on Emory University's Atlanta campus
items.description: Emory University reported an active shooter on its Atlanta, Georgia, campus on Friday.

items.title: LIVE:  ABC News Live
items.description: 24/7 coverage of breaking news and live events

items.title: Trump says he'll meet with Putin next Friday in Alaska
items.description: President Donald Trump has set Friday as a deadline for Russia's Vladimir Putin to agree to a ceasefire with Ukraine or face secondary sanctions.
